ore 8 TeV LHC data becomes available, the information\non individual Higgs boson production and decay processes provided by the CMS\nand ATLAS experiments can be effectively used to favour mUED or exclude it\nfurther.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Jul 2012 19:45:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Aug 2012 13:35:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 Dec 2012 01:07:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-30"}
