o for\n2-Facility Location on more general metric spaces, which is true even for\nsimple instances with 3 agents located in a star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jul 2012 10:06:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-05"}
